title: Face Editor Premium v4.4 (CTRC)
description:
[center][img]http://i.imgur.com/46HfCMJ.png[/img]


[b]Requirements:[/b] 3.0+

[b]Overview:[/b] FACE EDITOR SPECIFIC FEATURES FOR PORTRAITS & SELFIES

[b]Face Makeover like a pro:[/b]

[u]Lipstick & Makeup[/u] - Add color to your lips and apply any shade of powder
[u]Reshape[/u] - Perfect smile, Raise cheekbones, Enlarge eyes, Reshape nose
[u]Clone[/u] - Hide pimples, Remove background objects, Fix stray hair
[u]Focus[/u] - Make your face stand out by blurring the background
[u]Smooth wrinkles with a touch of a finger and rejuvenate your skin[/u]
[u]Make teeth whiter[/u]
[u]Remove bags below eyes[/u]
[u]Diet[/u] - Make entire image look thinner and taller

[b]POWERFUL PHOTO EDITOR[/b]

[u]Magazine[/u]-level photo touch up and editing
[u]Unlimited undo & redo,[/u] go back to every change you ever made
Full fledged photo editor that puts the power of Photoshop in your hand
[u]Filters[/u] - Standard filters for a professional look
[u]Lighting[/u] - Add lighting, enhance color and contrast
[u]Stickers[/u] - a variety of over 100 stickers, tattoos, labels and emojis
[u]Text[/u] - Over 50 fonts and text effects

[b]Draw over your image[/b]

[u]Rotate & Crop[/u] the image to include only parts you need.
[u]Frames[/u] - More than 30 frames that add a pro look to any photo or portrait
[u]Red-eye[/u] - Remove red-eye with a single touch
[/center]
